<SYNC Start=1831520><P Class=KRCC>
잘 꾸며 놨군요
<SYNC Start=1834440><P Class=KRCC>
멋있어요
<SYNC Start=1838001><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1843920><P Class=KRCC>
인상적이에요
